UID:10013846-1781119800-1781127000@visityolo.com
SUMMARY:Nigel Wearne Live @ The Melon Ball
DESCRIPTION:Watermelon Music in Davis presents Nigel Wearne. \nNigel Wearne saunters after dark in the music of the night\, blending blues\, jazz and Americana-noir. Hailing from Gunditjmara country in the deep south of Australia\, he’s a guitarist and multi-instrumentalist with diverse influences such as Nick Cave\, Tom Waits and Rickie Lee Jones. \nNigel has played some of the world’s most prestigious music festivals\, including Hardly Strictly Bluegrass\, MerleFest\, Philadelphia Folk Festival\, Adelaide Guitar Festival (AUS)\, 30A Songwriters Festival\, Bristol Rhythm & Roots Reunion and the Cambridge Folk Festival (UK). In 2025\, he won the Telluride Blues Challenge at the Telluride Blues & Brews Festival. \nHis sophomore album\, ‘Black Crow’ garnered wide critical acclaim including a 4-STAR review in Rolling Stone\, a nomination for Best Country Album at the Music Victoria Awards and it debuted at #1 on Australia’s AMRAP Charts. His 2023 album\, ‘The Reckoning’ received back-to-back nominations for Best Blues Work at the 2023 & 2024 Music Victoria Awards and a 4-STAR review in The Australian. 2025 marked a return to his roots as a folk songwriter with his latest album ‘The Lone Reckoning’. A raw\, emotive\, stripped back rendition of his 2023 award-nominated album ‘The Reckoning’. \nA deep thinker and truth seeker with a penchant for all things peculiar\, he sings of human frailty\, grace and the cosmos; songwriting that cuts to the bone. \n\n“Django Reinhardt with a cowboy twist” – Grateful Web UK.\n“Tailor made for fans of Tom Waits” – Rhythms Magazine.\n“Poignant and mysterious” – Maverick Magazine UK.\n“Vocal swagger of Van Morrison and dark spirituality and intelligence of Nick Cave” 4 STARS – The Australian.\n\n$20 General Admission\nDoors open at 7:00pm \nNigel Wearne Links:\nwww.nigelwearne.com\nwww.instagram.com/nigelwearne\nwww.youtube.com/nigelwearne\nwww.facebook.com/nigelwearnemusic\nhttps://open.spotify.com/artist/46borjrmKCaBVcb2SMBNHe\nhttps://music.apple.com/us/artist/nigel-wearne/561843931 https://tidal.com/browse/artist/4720696
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/nigel-wearne-live-the-melon-ball/
LOCATION:Watermelon Music\, 1970 Lake Blvd\, DAVIS\, CA\, 95616\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/061026TICKET.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Watermelon Music":MAILTO:info@watermelonmusic.com
END:VEVENT
